data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to this stunning property with a serene natural color palette, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. Boasting several rooms for flexible living space, this home offers endless possibilities to customize and adapt to your lifestyle. The primary bathroom features a separate tub and shower, perfect for relaxation after a long day, as well as double sinks for added convenience. Ample under sink storage ensures a clutter-free space. Step outside to a covered sitting area in the backyard, the ideal spot for enjoying fresh air and entertaining guests. With fresh interior and exterior paint, this home exudes a bright and modern feel. Partial flooring replacement in select areas adds a touch of freshness to the space. Additionally, this property is equipped with brand new appliances, making daily tasks a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your own!
